  <td>
  <p>SU</p>
  <p>Sunday</p>
  </td>
  <td>
  <p>If set to 1, specifies that the task can run on
  Sunday.</p>
  </td>
 </tr><tr>
  <td>
  <p>MO</p>
  <p>Monday</p>
  </td>
  <td>
  <p>If set to 1, specifies that the task can run on
  Monday.</p>
  </td>
 </tr><tr>
  <td>
  <p>TU</p>
  <p>Tuesday</p>
  </td>
  <td>
  <p>If set to 1, specifies that the task can run on
